column5: Tim Horton's early batch would be jealous of this fish's freshness.  Fresher then people off the boat (fob) Wat a fight!!!!!   I thought a locomotive snagged my fish the way this beauty was fighting.  Sweet colouration, and a non healed open wound lamprey eel mark.  First lucky skill drift 30" chunkster    A hen tricked into submission sooner then immediately   Who needs crack with joy like this????
thats a cool report and those are some real nice bows....,man is that little hen ever silver
That hurts to see as I sit here at work, Dang - Nice fish.  Joey
Great job again!!! I always look forward to reading your posts and viewing your pics....thanks!  With the weather the way it is, I have a feeling I'll be seeing them all thru the winter!
I wish i could fish as often as you. Nice fish man
